See Numerics/Optimisation.hpp for the general information.

A) Black-box use

See

https://nomad-4-user-guide.readthedocs.io/en/latest/GettingStarted.html#getting-started

for a basic introduction, not using the library-mode, but just writing
free-standing C++ programs, which

 - take the parameters from a file (space-separated)
 - output the result plus the constraints-values on standard output.
